http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Two-youth-create-ruckus-thrashed-by-public/article13997310.ece

Irate public thrashed two youth and set fire to their bikes after they started attacking passers-by in an inebriated state in RPC Layout, Vijaynagar, in the early hours of Wednesday.The two youth, identified as Rajesh and Prajwal, created ruckus after parking their bike in the middle of the road. They attacked a few passers-by who questioned their behaviour. Enraged by this the residents who gathered by the time chased and thrashed the youth before handing them over to the police. A few people also set fire to the bike.The police detained the duo for questioning.